# Silver Balladeer
Alignment							KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Alignment		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DESC:A silver balladeer must have a good alignment. This ability alters alignment.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.115
Bardic Performance					KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Bardic Performance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DESC:A silver balladeer gains the bardic performances listed below. These bardic performances all require the use of a silver or silver-stringed instrument, which costs twice as much as a normal masterwork instrument.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.115
Break Curse							KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Break Curse		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 6th level, a silver balladeer can suppress a single curse affecting an ally within 30 feet that is able to see and hear her. Each round the silver balladeer uses break curse, she attempts a Perform check against the original DC of the curse. If successful, she suppresses the curse for 1 round. After she has suppressed the curse for 4 consecutive rounds, she can attempt a caster level check to remove the curse as if she had cast remove curse. This ability replaces suggestion.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.115
Holy Vibration						KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Holy Vibration	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 9th level, a silver balladeer can spend a round of bardic performance to make a single door or a window within 30 feet resonate with a holy vibration. Undead and creatures with the evil subtype are unable to open a door or window affected in this way (as arcane lock) for 10 minutes per bard level. If such a creature has the incorporeal subtype, it is unable to move through the affected door or window, or through any walls, floors, or ceilings within 20 feet of it. Incorporeal creatures can attempt Charisma checks to break through areas warded by holy vibration, using the same break DC as for the object the creature is trying to move through. This ability replaces inspire greatness.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.115
Mass Break Curse						KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Mass Break Curse	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 18th level, a silver balladeer can suppress all curses among any number of allies within 30 feet when using break curse. Every 4 consecutive rounds of using this performance, the silver balladeer can attempt a caster level check to remove a single curse on a single ally affected by this performance, as if she had cast remove curse. This ability replaces mass suggestion.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.115
Pure Heart							KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Pure Heart		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:At 2nd level, a silver balladeer gains a +4 bonus on saving throws against curses, hexes, and charm effects. This ability replaces well-versed.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.116
Silver Mastery						KEY:Silver Balladeer ~ Silver Mastery	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Silver Balladeer Class Feature.Bard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:At 2nd level, a silver balladeer treats silver weapons as if they were also cold iron for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction. Also, alchemical silver weapons do not impose a penalty on damage rolls when wielded by a silver balladeer, and a silver balladeer gains a +1 bonus on attack rolls made with mithral weapons. This ability replaces the 2nd-level versatile performance.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.116


